name: BookingHunter
overview: BookingHunter.com is a travel search engine that allows consumers to compare prices on hotels, flights, car rental, hostel anf activities. The search engine aggregates results from more than 200 travel websites simultaneously to give an overview of the best offers found. The site is multilingual, offering travel searches in over 9 languages including Chinese, Russian, Portuguese, Spanish and Japanese. BookingHunter.com does not sell directly; instead, the site can be used to find the cheapest deal after which users are automatically transferred to the travel supplier’s website to make their booking directly.
